{"tid":485231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[即刻駁嘴]如果香港合法化左叫雞，對社會有咩影響？","createTime":"2017-11-30T19:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T21:02:10.000Z","uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"151d1df830f74392efa7fdacd76cbcd28d15dfd8","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:00:29.000Z","msg":"眼見澳洲又合法左，日本又係，起到諗香港合法埋會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n壞處我只係諗到道德淪亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d00e530439fd15e2582332bc7538e0aa36022b","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:02:50.000Z","msg":"有諗過會唔會增加性病傳染率,但政府合法得個監控都要做足，好似日本咁，所以可以駁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a5aa8c102df2610324414cc8b11f592a1c5f9a","tid":485231,"uid":42364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:03:25.000Z","msg":"香港叫雞合化架喎"},{"pid":"700af6a4ff84221d4f246cc1e8995aacccb95a02","tid":485231,"uid":51978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:10:15.000Z","msg":"香港叫雞幾時唔合法？<br />\n<br />\n樓豬你on9少陣啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀緊llb"},{"pid":"f6b8fcceb087be7872c5c7858975410250677b87","tid":485231,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"訓啦傻閪柒頭"},{"pid":"81d1795739dd1bee9d0d2baafa8f33bec64b9b61","tid":485231,"uid":138375,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"屌 無常識唔緊要 唔好揚出黎先得架"},{"pid":"bf10ee3242670a479241a83bf0ad210b8d234be8","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港叫雞幾時唔合法？<br />\n<br />\n樓豬你on9少陣啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀緊llb</blockquote><br />\n唔係仲未全面合法化咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔犯法但亦都唔係合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0427b573f3f1b0c49f8fe0899109094e55a9bce9","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:43:58.000Z","msg":"人地全面合法左政府係會監管，雖然香港你叫唔犯法，但香港政府對啲雞都冇監管<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     聽人咁講，我唔知所以放上黎問下學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a60bbab8629f191a938dee5f3bd05cab820a72","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:01:53.000Z","msg":"合法化是指發牌認可妓院內的賣淫活動。這個做法，承認妓院是正當商業機構， 在城市規劃中，可以合法使用土地設置合法經營。<br />\n<br />\n而賣淫婦女須要註冊，並須接受定期性病及愛滋病檢查。<br />\n<br />\n香港的性交易本身是合法的，但有組織的性交易是非法的。<br />\n一樓一鳳：香港性工作者在自家住宅提供色情服務的獨有方式，因為在一個住宅單位內只有一名妓女而名。如單一個地方只有一個性工作者靠提供性服務換取報酬便不算犯法<br />\n<br />\n夜總會、卡拉OK伴唱、性感按摩館：通常此類場所在場內只提供合法娛樂。真正性交易會在場外（例如時鐘酒店）進行。"},{"pid":"084915b8b1b43e41dfa53cb890a64b39453f93ce","tid":485231,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:02:54.000Z","msg":"唔係合法既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係無身份証做雞既就犯法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ddc9e183f1435737eff6dd9a660eb47fbef1fe","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係合法既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係無身份証做雞既就犯法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇資料的確冇話係犯法，但政府又唔係全面合法晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9a789fca1295c2063ca37af2c47671d0fdaea0","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:10:00.000Z","msg":"經營色情場所和操控性工作者在香港是違法的，因此出現了不少利用法律漏洞提供性服務的場所。<br />\n<br />\n除了一樓一鳳外，其他均是違法的。<br />\n<br />\n如果全面合法左就唔會只局限一樓一啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90efe29d5a5016de650e13cb592dfacfaf74dea","tid":485231,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:13:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da6ec744c125df4de43a8936b240e3b609c9169a","tid":485231,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港叫雞幾時唔合法？<br />\n<br />\n樓豬你on9少陣啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀緊llb</blockquote><br />\n唔係仲未全面合法化咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔犯法但亦都唔係合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係合法，一係唔合法<br />\n<br />\n點樣又合法又唔合法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c9efbcd8d688c91e2089981c3e375ad906924","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依靠妓女為生先係犯法，一樓一同嫖妓都係合法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但點解經營色情場所就會違<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    一樓一話係自己屋企先吹佢唔脹   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51530e4ff12a9665043d49508b64ec63a97afe26","tid":485231,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港叫雞幾時唔合法？<br />\n<br />\n樓豬你on9少陣啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀緊llb</blockquote><br />\n唔係仲未全面合法化咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔犯法但亦都唔係合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係合法，一係唔合法<br />\n<br />\n點樣又合法又唔合法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i